# web-specific build-context filter. Keeps the Next image build context tight
# so `docker build -f web/Dockerfile .` doesn't haul up the entire repo.

# build artifacts
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/node_modules

# test + tooling outputs
**/coverage
**/playwright-report
**/.playwright-mcp
**/tsconfig.tsbuildinfo

# tests aren't needed for the production bundle
web/tests
web/e2e
web/playwright.config.ts

# editor / OS noise
**/.DS_Store
**/.idea
**/.vscode
**/*.log

# secrets — never ship a stray .env into the image
**/.env
**/.env.*
!web/.env.example
